{"tid":2106153,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"China ranked #1  !?","createTime":"2020-07-13T07:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T10:56:40.000Z","uid":310461,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e458a7b4cdeccc82b92d96784ef210a71ef340a9","tid":2106153,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:04:50.000Z","msg":"In the opening speech, it was mentioned that China was<span class=\"violet\"> ranked #1 by World Bank in 2 years.</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwObARZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwObARZ.jpg&h=6a26cd5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sxcaTj2Utfc?t=224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsxcaTj2Utfc%3Ft%3D224&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=1ac88850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sxcaTj2Utfc?t=224</a><br />\n<br />\nI could only find China was<span class=\"violet\"><strong> ranked  #31 and #46</strong></span> in the last 2 years by World Bank.  Instead, New Zealand score #1 in the last 2 years. <br />\n <br />\nPlease correct me if I have missed something.  Highly ranked officials must have some data which could not be found in public or internet....<ins></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uSLF1P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uSLF1P.jpg&h=029572a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;.....The irony is that the World Bank needs China more than China needs the World Bank.....&quot; (<a href=\"http://tiny.cc/ej1csz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2Fej1csz&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=27a1aeb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tiny.cc/ej1csz</a>)  I am not sure if there is any implications too on the statistics....."},{"pid":"b05ac0420bcc2aa5b254bf2c7518844b21ea1eff","tid":2106153,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike"